headline: New PAM Air Fryer Spray a Must-Have for Air Fryer Owners
summary: As the leader in cooking sprays1, PAM® Cooking Spray, a brand of Conagra Brands, Inc. (NYSE: CAG), has been an essential tool for home cooks and professional chefs for more than 60 years. Now PAM has introduced a new formula specifically designed for one of America's most-popular kitchen appliances – the air fryer.
